{{refimprove|date=January 2017}}
[[Jimmie Johnson]] is an American racing driver who won seven [[Monster Energy NASCAR Cup Series]] championships. Over the course of his racing career, Johnson has won multiple races, 83 of which were in NASCAR's top level.
==NASCAR==
===Monster Energy NASCAR Cup Series=== In the Cup Series, Jimmie Johnson, the seven-time champion, has won 83 races. He's won at 20 different tracks. Johnson's 83 wins rank tied sixth with [[Cale Yarborough]] on the all-time wins.
