{{TOC right|limit=2}} {{Lists of Turkish people}} This is a list of [[WP:Notability|notable]] [[Turkish people]], or the Turks, (Turkish: Türkler), who are an ethnic group primarily living in the republic of Turkey and in the former lands of the Ottoman Empire where Turkish minorities have been established. They include people of Turkish descent born in other countries whose roots are in those countries. For [[Ottoman Empire|Ottoman]] people see [[List of Ottoman people]].
